{"tid":174513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呢啲係咪雙重標準？只許蔣公捉錯，不準人妻指正？","createTime":"2017-03-27T00:28:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T02:04:25.000Z","uid":90,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"30c1821513b4a4992cb1df9c372d6d49bb8564be","tid":174513,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T00:28:34.000Z","msg":"事源見蔣公捉人錯字，話其他人係大陸仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/27/082437_7a5c39143c7e95de564abfc76c618b18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F27%2F082437_7a5c39143c7e95de564abfc76c618b18.jpg&h=3072c503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但係我又發現佢打錯字啵<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/27/082546_c613cfd6919a82b70e63ab3749484633.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F27%2F082546_c613cfd6919a82b70e63ab3749484633.jpg&h=9c357700&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/742x6X0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F742x6X0.jpg&h=c93c8454&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/27/082554_d26c83aa17e45b959499a50287957c08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F27%2F082554_d26c83aa17e45b959499a50287957c08.jpg&h=30a1d4dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我話佢個時，就見我去驗腦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/27/082711_45077f5a87a1ff32eb685e5c9776bae9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F27%2F082711_45077f5a87a1ff32eb685e5c9776bae9.jpg&h=820cd035&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人地個啲錯就係人地嘅錯<br />\n蔣公嘅錯係人地嘅錯"},{"pid":"738ac494d768187ec845eb369c82979b92555efc","tid":174513,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T